\code{wheel}, \code{resize}) → \code{wire_throttle(100)} (paced "latest position"
stream, with the derived \code{coalesce = TRUE} keeping it from outrunning the
server); every other event → \code{wire_immediate()}. Explicit \code{timing} always
wins over the default.
